data.description: Discover this ideal beautiful home in Silver Firs!Inside this charming home enjoy the spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and an adjoining dining room for relaxation.The family room features a cozy fireplace, setting the mood for gatherings.The kitchen boasts granite countertops and a convenient peninsula bar for casual dining.Upstairs, the large primary bedroom includes an ensuite with 2 walk-in closets for ample storage. Located near Mill Creek, you'll have easy access to shopping and the YMCA for fitness and fun. Explore miles of walking trails, parks, and sports courts. With community events throughout the year, Silver Firs offers a welcoming and vibrant atmosphere.This home is your gateway to a balanced and connected lifestyle.
